{"tid":706471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路維：德國輸在緊張","createTime":"2018-06-18T02:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T16:38:21.000Z","uid":33799,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"340cba96e783fbd2c84430f21f67ecbcec447025","tid":706471,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=jdNRKCjb3sKG7K77ecYh1HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=af7162b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】上屆世界盃冠軍德國展開衛冕之旅，以0:1惜敗墨西哥，落筆打三更，主帥路維失望表示：「輸在緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n4屆世界盃冠軍德國爆出今屆最大冷門，F組首戰遭遇滑鐵盧，主帥路維（Joachim Low）賽後表示：「這場我們無法踢出應有水準，上半場表現緊張，賽後必須檢討原因。」 「上半場，我們失去應有的跑動能力。」德國半場落後0:1，下半場狂攻之下，碌碌無為，路維分析指：「下半場，我不太滿意己隊對抗性不足。」 「作為世界盃的球員，你一定要懂受比賽上的壓力。」路維<span style=\"color: red;\">透露無意改變套路</span>：「比賽輸了，但我們一定不會改變原來的部署，無論如何，球隊必須保持自己的長處，如球員比賽時看得不夠通透，便會失去控球權。」<br />\n<br />\nDraxler邊忽緊張呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180618/large/1529259919_4d15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F1529259919_4d15.jpg&h=1035f5ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d13cab81a9a15015a14520d82391da99088e5eb8","tid":706471,"uid":9298,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"中場猜猜下波都俾人偷到，次次防守反擊都差唔多搞掂...如果唔係條友浪射的話..."},{"pid":"f1eef4ba85bdc45637797af973d85116c9a85f5e","tid":706471,"uid":127347,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"緊乜張呀，世界盃都拎過啦，緊乜張？緊張輸左波無雞叫炸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262531a271997e5250de1efcb68d658b2837e786","tid":706471,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"正 又有得睇達斯拿"},{"pid":"b6